sroots meet the summit team get to know us what binds us safetyit’s our culture and ingrained in everything we do it’s protecting our best assets  our people responsibilitydoing it right the first time standing behind our products and services to meet the needs of our customers opportunitymaintaining a local presence to bring growth to and connect with our communities our storysummit materials was formed in  when tom hill and a small team of investors with a bold vision formed a new kind of building materials company the company was founded around a single simple idea to bring successful companies together into something even greater summit brings value to its family of companies by maintaining entrepreneurial spirit and local presence while providing access to resources and shared best practices since summits formation the company has completed more than  acquisitions forming  platform companies operating in  states and british columbia canada these companies provide aggregates cement readymix asphalt and construction services to meet residential nonresidential and public demand meet our family news summit materials announces second quarter  results conference call date summit materials to attend upcoming investor conferences all news events there are currently no upcoming events full calendar contact our acquisition team contact now materials  construction materials  summit materials jump to navigation summit materials materials we see opportunity around every corner to help build your communitysourced from the highest quality sites efficient production for consistency and strength integrated product offering to our customers summit materials is a vertically integrated construction materials company that produces aggregates cement readymix concrete and asphalt and offers paving construction and other services   these types of products and services touch almost every aspect of your daily life from the roads you drive to work to the cell phone you use to call home building materials fact concrete has been used in some form since roman times it is the most universal construction material today our materials aggregatesaggregates are the building blocks of our nation’s construction industry these natural resources are the foundation of products and services that develop our public and private infrastructure the aggregate materials are sourced from our quarries and are the key materials in production of asphalt concrete and cement we stand behind the process and quality from rock to road cementcement when combined with aggregates and water produces concrete cement is the binder that makes concrete durable weather resistant and adaptable our state of the art cement plant and production process enable our companies and our customers to offer superior concrete products readymixreadymix is a highly versatile construction material that can be used to make everything from curbs to kitchen counters its flexible recipe characteristics allow for an end product that can assume almost any color shape texture and strength readymix concrete can be customized to suit your needs asphaltasphalt is one of the most common roadway materials used today approximately  percent of our nations roads are paved with asphalt it is formed by the combination of aggregates and liquid asphalt asphalt is  percent renewable and the us alone recycles nearly  million tons of asphalt each year   paving constructionpaving is the final stage of summit’s vertically integrated product offering our companies perform quality work that complements our materials by providing a downstream outlet to distribute these products our skilled labor force and quality service offering provide a one stop shop to our customers our process site planninga site is chosen to be sustainable throughout and beyond extraction before the first stone is removed we are already planning for the lifecycle of the site safe extractionwe partner with our neighbors and our legislators to work responsibly in our environment throughout the extraction process site repurposingas the last stone is removed a site’s lifecycle progresses as it continues to provide communities with varying types of future development news summit materials announces second quarter  results conference call date summit materials to attend upcoming investor conferences all news events there are currently no upcoming events full calendar contact our acquisition team contact now summit materials llc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et construction materials company overview of summit materials llc snapshot people company overview summit materials llc together with its subsidiaries operates as a construction materials company in the united states and canada it company operates through the west east and cement segments the company produces and sells aggregates cement readymixed concrete and asphalt paving mix as well as concrete products and plastics components it also provides paving and related services as of december   the company operated  quarries and sand deposits  cement plants  cement distribution terminals  fixed and portable readymix concrete plants and  asphalt paving mix plants as well as landfill sites it serves public infrastructure residential construction and non summit materials llc together with its subsidiaries operates as a construction materials company in the united states and canada it company operates through the west east and cement segments the company produces and sells aggregates cement readymixed concrete and asphalt paving mix as well as concrete products and plastics components it also provides paving and related services as of december   the company operated  quarries and sand deposits  cement plants  cement distribution terminals  fixed and portable readymix concrete plants and  asphalt paving mix plants as well as landfill sites it serves public infrastructure residential construction and nonresidential construction markets the company was founde